text: Družstevník Liptovská Štiavnica is a Slovak football team, based in the village of Liptovská Štiavnica. The club was founded in 1932. ==References== == External links == *Official website Druzstevnik Liptovska Stiavnica Category:Association football clubs established in 1932
title: TJ Družstevník Liptovská Štiavnica
